It's an example to simualte neutron from dd gun and scatter in heavy water and pass a Fe fliter to choose mono energy neutron.
Geant4 version is 10.6.2 and root version is 6.28, python version is 3.9.
You can run:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake../
make
cd ..
mkdir out
chmod +x run_scrip.sh
./run_scrip.sh

You can merge all root files into one csv file by python merge.py if you want.
In this program, you can just run ./toyMC for the visiaul window, or you can run ./toyMC outfile_name logfile_name, like run_scrip.sh.
